sci_fi_and_fantasy.title: Sci-fi & Fantasy
sci_fi_and_fantasy.description: No need to travel to a galaxy, far, far away — all the space odysseys, fantastic voyages, and close encounters that you seek are right here.

274712.title: Little Bear Movie
274712.description: Inspired by the classic children's book, a young bear and his father go camping and make a new friend who sets them off on a series of adventures.

281661.title: Cloned: The Recreator Chronicles
281661.description: When a group of teenagers stumble upon a secret lab, they come face to face with exact copies, duplicates of themselves. But what if your clone was a far superior version of yourself, would you kill it, or let it replace you?

283992.title: Redline
283992.description: In this animated high-speed thrill, a daredevil driver and his secret love face off in the most dangerous and exciting car race in the universe.

286029.title: Bad Johnson
286029.description: As punishment for his behavior, a womanizer’s penis magically leaves his body to become human. To get his penis back, he must redeem himself.

289793.title: Dead Space: Downfall
289793.description: A group of deep space miners discover an ancient artifact while on a mission to a faraway planet, accidentally releasing an unusual alien race.

299583.title: The Darkest Hour
299583.description: In this tense apocalyptic thriller, five youths fight to survive after being stranded in Moscow during an alien attack.

324817.title: Jules Verne's Mysterious Island
324817.description: Commandeering a hot air balloon in a desperate escape, five Union POWs drift onto an odd island…populated with things of which they’d never dreamed.

332938.title: Repo: The Genetic Opera
332938.description: In 2056, an epidemic of organ failures devastates the planet and those who cannot afford their treatments are hunted by villainous Repo Men.

342067.title: Zapped
342067.description: A teenager who struggles to adjust to her new stepfamily and school receives some help when a dog training app gives her the power to control boys.

367626.title: 2012: Doomsday
367626.description: As the date of the apocalypse nears, several strangers travel to a temple in Mexico to prevent an ancient prophecy from destroying the world.

417720.title: Tekken
417720.description: In 2039, when territories are run by corporations, a warrior rises from the streets to avenge his mother's death by entering a fighting competition.

441247.title: Wish Upon a Star
441247.description: A younger sister wishes to switch places with her popular older sister and the two bickering siblings awaken to find the wish has come true.

456664.title: 2036: Origin Unknown
456664.description: A shrewd astronaut works with her ship's artificial intelligence system to uncover the mystery behind an unknown object found on Mars.

463838.title: The Last Unicorn
463838.description: A brave unicorn and a magician fight an evil king who is obsessed with attempting to capture the world's unicorns.

464288.title: Returned
464288.description: A missing man returns 12 years after his flight disappeared, searching for answers with the assistance of a beautiful and mysterious woman.

465295.title: Guardians (English Dub)
465295.description: Formed during the Cold War, an elite squad of superheroes return to action when new threats arise that threaten the safety of the world.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

466386.title: Daylight's End
466386.description: In a future teeming with blood-hungry creatures, a rogue drifter reluctantly agrees to help a band of survivors find their way to a safe haven.

466956.title: Thunder and the House of Magic
466956.description: A lost cat finds shelter in the enchanted home of a retired magician but the man’s scheming nephew also has some tricks up his sleeve.

467588.title: The Man From Earth
467588.description: When colleagues throw a farewell bash for a retiring professor, the scholar reveals that he's had a stranger and far, far longer past than they knew.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

475643.title: Stargate
475643.description: A historical expert and a military unit travel through a mysterious portal. They land in a bizarre world occupied by a dangerous and powerful being.

476764.title: Atlantic Rim: Resurrection
476764.description: When massive, weaponized monsters emerge from the sea and threaten LA, a group of humans pilot giant robots, trying to save the city and the world.

484424.title: June
484424.description: An ancient demon possesses the body of a nine-year-old girl and it’s up to her foster parents to fight for their daughter and the fate of mankind.

489692.title: Post Impact
489692.description: After a cataclysmic meteor strike hurls Earth into a new ice age, a few survivors search for others and a device that promises new hope for humankind.

493465.title: Ice Twisters
493465.description: A scientist who becomes a science fiction author finds himself living the plot of one his novels when federal weather experiments go haywire.

507612.title: Monster Hunt 2
507612.description: The exciting sequel follows the heroic Wuba after he parts ways with his human parents and seeks to restore peace within the monster world.

507852.title: Above the Shadows
507852.description: A woman who became literally invisible to others after her mother died works as a sleuth until meeting a jaded fighter, the only one who can see her.

514216.title: Time Lapse
514216.description: Three friends scheming to misuse a mysterious machine that takes photos 24 hours into the future begin to see disturbing and scary pictures develop.

517420.title: End of the World
517420.description: Natural disasters tear apart Los Angeles, as a father and daughter attempt to evade the solar storms, tsunamis, volcanoes, and flooding.

519423.title: Earthfall
519423.description: When a massive asteroid pulls Earth out of orbit and wreaks chaos on the ground, one man uncovers the secret government plan that could save humanity.

524652.title: Coherence
524652.description: When eight friends gather for a dinner party on the night of an astronomical event, a series of unusual circumstances tests their relationships.

526872.title: The Librarian: Curse of the Judas Chalice
526872.description: A mild-mannered scholar scours mystical New Orleans to find an ancient silver cup, rumored to have the power to bring a Romanian vampire back to life.

526874.title: The Librarian: Return to King Solomon's Mines
526874.description: A lovable antiquities scholar and a brainy archaeologist hunt for a legendary holy book, but must elude a sinister general and a scheming uncle.

527553.title: The Librarian: Quest for the Spear
527553.description: A student working at the New York Public Library discovers historical treasures. Now, he must guard them from powerful forces of evil.

530235.description: While feeling unfulfilled and stuck in a rut, a man finds intimacy and companionship when he learns about a technological advancement called Sexbots.

535991.title: Contención (Doblado)
535991.description: Despiertan con la novedad de que sus puertas y ventanas están selladas: una cuarentana obligatoria sin luz, ni agua ni comunicación con el exterior.

538002.title: Wild Witch
538002.description: The simple scratch from a black cat unleashes the power of 12-year-old Clara, who becomes a wild witch destined to rid the world of an ancient evil.

539674.title: Independence Daysaster
539674.description: When Earth is attacked by hostile aliens, a firefighter and a rogue scientist team up to build the only weapon capable of defeating the attackers.

543774.title: Tornado Warning
543774.description: A team of experts race to stop extraterrestrials that appear as destructive "electrical tornadoes" on Earth.

550824.title: The Hunger Games
550824.description: In a dystopian future, 16-year-old Katniss volunteers to take her younger sister’s place in a battle where children must fight to stay alive.

550826.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
550826.description: As Katniss and Peeta embark on their victory tour, President Snow plans an even deadlier new Hunger Games, which threatens the future of Panem.

550828.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 2
550828.description: The celebrated movie series reaches its epic climax, as the brave Katniss fights to liberate Panem's citizens in a final showdown with President Snow.

551255.title: The Hunger Games: Mockingjay Part 1
551255.description: The franchise phenomenon continues, as Katniss, having survived The Hunger Games, rises with District 13 to battle the oppressive President Snow.

552502.title: The Final Countdown
552502.description: America's most powerful nuclear-run aircraft carrier is transported back in time to December 6, 1941, hours prior to the attack on Pearl Harbor.

555823.title: Trucks
555823.description: It’s man against machine in this Stephen King-penned joy ride in which a small truck stop town is conquered by a mob of homicidal autonomous trucks.

559759.description: A paralyzing flash of light and sound that comes every day at the same time begins to destroy the life of a New York City air traffic controller.

561256.title: Thor: End of Days
561256.description: Norse god Thor chases the power-hungry Loki, but needs a female human’s aid, when he awakens on Earth without his mighty hammer or his memory.

563016.title: Invasion Planet Earth
563016.description: A gigantic alien fleet launches a devastating attack on Earth. The ultimate war for Planet Earth is about to begin, and only one man can save it.

565419.title: Chabelo Y Pepito en La Lámpara Maravillosa
565419.description: Pepito tendrá que evitar que la lámpara que compró, y que inesperadamente le concede toda clase de deseos, caiga en las malas manos de su padrastro.

565697.title: The Last Scout
565697.description: Following the destruction of Earth, a team of astronauts battles the elements and scours the universe to find an inhabitable new home for mankind.

569769.title: Pandorum
569769.description: Panic and terror come fast as two astronauts wake up in an empty spacecraft with no memory of what happened - except that an evil entity is waiting.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

573585.title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
573585.description: When a young man receives his grandfather’s distress signal from a remote island, he heads off with his stepfather and a helicopter tour team.

577102.title: Dune Drifter
577102.description: After a devastating orbital space battle against an armada of unbeatable enemy ships, the survivor of a crashed star-fighter navigates the harsh surface of a planet to save herself before her life support expires.

577924.title: Arthur and the Invisibles
577924.description: After his grandfather disappears, a boy enlists the help of mysterious little people to save his family home from emerging real estate developers.

581682.title: Stargate: Continuum
581682.description: The popular TV series ‘Stargate SG-1’ continues in this film reuniting key characters in a new world where their past victories have been erased.

587321.title: Occupation
587321.description: When alien invaders threaten mankind, a group of random townspeople must band together and fight back against the vicious extraterrestrials.

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

594963.title: Valhalla - The Legend of Thor
594963.description: Together with Thor and Loki, two siblings fight to save Valhalla from the end of the world in Ragnarok.

595780.title: Scales: Mermaids Are Real
595780.description: A young girl faces the bittersweet reality that, on her upcoming twelfth birthday, she is destined to turn into a mermaid.

602633.title: Attraction (Dubbed)
602633.description: A spaceship’s catastrophic crash into Moscow sends the population into terrified chaos while an alien offers a young woman a new state of existence.

602966.title: Attraction 2: Invasion (Dubbed)
602966.description: After an encounter with an alien craft, a young woman begins to acquire superpowers that put a target on her back by extraterrestrials and humans.

604334.title: Viking Destiny
604334.description: A Viking Princess travels the world gaining wisdom and building the army she needs to win back her throne.

605250.title: Coma
605250.description: After an accident, a young architect wakes up to a chaotic, physics-defying dystopian world and joins a band of rogue fighters to find an escape.

607451.title: E.T. The Extra-Terrestrial
607451.description: A boy forms a special bond with a sweet and gifted alien from another planet. He tries to keep it a secret, but he needs help to keep the visitor safe.

610510.title: Anunnaki
610510.description: A review of scientific research that looks back on mankind’s ancestors, who are said to have descended from a heavenly realm to create human beings.

611206.title: The 13th Warrior
611206.description: Far from home, an exiled ambassador joins a fierce band of Viking warriors, who are attacked by ferocious creatures that devour every living thing.

627349.title: Godzilla vs. Mechagodzilla (Dubbed)
627349.description: Godzilla finds himself in battle with his cosmic double bent on fulfilling an Okinawan prophecy warning of Earth's destruction at the monster’s claws.

628970.title: Hellboy II: The Golden Army
628970.description: Hellboy and his crew of paranormal outcasts face off with forces of darkness in this imaginative adventure from visionary director Guillermo del Toro.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

634414.title: Rapture
634414.description: Survivors of an apocalypse seek refuge while grappling with a poisoned food and water supply, killer lighting, and robed figures vaporizing all life.

637860.title: The Cosmic Hoax
637860.description: Various experts make a case regarding official UFO disclosures and secrecy that implies manipulation of the public by the military-industrial complex.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

639868.title: Swamp Thing
639868.description: After a violent incident with a special chemical, a research scientist who is trying to create a new life form is turned into a swamp plant monster.

641581.title: Somewhere in Time
641581.description: A playwright visiting a hotel falls in love with an actress pictured in a 1912 photo and uses self-hypnosis to go 68 years back in time to meet her.

645956.title: Risen
645956.description: A terrifying end of days scenario threatens life and safety as we know it after a meteorite explosion contaminates an Australian farming town.

649963.title: Freaks
649963.description: A little girl who has been shut away from the outside world by her father soon discovers a dangerous universe awaiting beyond her front door.

651086.title: Hancock
651086.description: A sarcastic, hard-living, misunderstood superhero, whose antics caused him to fall out of favor with the public, saves someone who might save him.

655369.title: The Monkey King Reborn
655369.description: Monkey King is in a race against time to rescue Tang Monk before the King of Demons regains power and initiates his plan to destroy the Earth.

655371.title: Project Gemini
655371.description: Centuries of destroying Earth’s resources leaves humankind’s last chance at survival in space where an unimaginable force is lying in wait.

657094.title: Snake
657094.description: A biology teacher ltrying to save his ill daughter with a natural cure goes into the jungle with experts and finds a horror that's larger than life.

657430.title: La Guerra de los Mundos: Destrucción Total (Doblado)
657430.description: Tras una invasión alienígena, la única esperanza de supervivencia que tienen una madre y su hijo radica en el descubrimiento de una verdad impensable.

661142.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
661142.description: The third film in the Twilight franchise. Torn between Edward and Jacob, Bella must also confront a vengeful vampire and a string of grisly murders.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

661453.title: The Legend of the Five
661453.description: A group of misfit teenagers find a relic, which transports them to a magical forest where they must stop an age-old evil from destroying the world.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

666107.title: Status Update
666107.description: After his parents split up, a struggling teenager stumbles upon a life-altering, magical app that causes his social media updates to come true.

670370.title: Brightburn
670370.description: What if a child from another world crash-landed on Earth, but instead of becoming a hero to mankind, he proved to be something far more sinister?

672442.title: Dredd
672442.description: The head of Mega City One’s elite police force becomes the city’s last hope when a sex worker-turned-drug dealer aims to take over the city.

676858.title: 16 Wishes
676858.description: On her 16th birthday, Abby Jensen's every wish comes magically, wondrously true until one wish too many go wrong and alters everything.

677018.title: Only
677018.description: After a comet releases a mysterious plague threatening to kill all women on the planet, a couple is put to the ultimate test as they try to survive.

680467.title: Dead Zone
680467.description: To stop the collapse of humanity, an elite team of soldiers must descend on a radiation-poisoned town and perform the ultimate stealth mission using high-tech armor and weapons.

680579.title: Extraterrestrial
680579.description: A group of young friends on a weekend trip to a cabin in the woods find themselves terrorized by alien visitors after mistakenly making contact.

680735.title: Jason X
680735.description: Cryogenically frozen in the 21st century and left on an inhabitable Earth, the hockey-masked killer is thawed in 2455 for a new reign of terror.

682075.title: Switched
682075.description: Tired of being bullied, Cassandra prays that her nemesis, Katie, the queen bee of social media, would know what it's like to walk a day in her shoes.

683075.title: Shark Side of the Moon
683075.description: Decades ago, the USSR developed unkillable sharks and launched them to the moon. Today, a team of American astronauts will endure the fight of their lives.

684095.title: The Cobbler
684095.description: Tired of his life, Max the cobbler discovers a magical heirloom that allows him to turn into other people and see what life's like in their shoes.

684097.title: The Man Who Killed Hitler and Then the Bigfoot
684097.description: An American war hero who secretly assassinated Adolf Hitler is called back to duty by Uncle to take out another global threat: Bigfoot.

685616.title: Halo 4: Forward Unto Dawn
685616.description: UNSC Cadet Thomas Lasky must conquer his inner fears and join forces with super-soldier John-117 to take down a massive faction of the Covenant.

686278.title: Doom
686278.description: Based on the hit videogame, this adventure begins when a call for help from a research station on Mars sends a team of mercenary Marines into action.

689820.title: Max Winslow and the House of Secrets
689820.description: Five teenagers compete to win a billionaire scientist's mansion by facing off against the super computer that controls it.

693659.title: Archive
693659.description: 2038. A roboticist has been working on a human-equivalent android, with each prototype being an increasingly advanced version of his deceased wife.

696007.title: Impact
696007.description: During a 10,000-year meteor shower, a rogue asteroid smashes into the moon and causes disastrous electromagnetic anomalies of weightlessness on Earth.

698078.title: Apollo 18
698078.description: Decades-old found footage involving three astronauts and an abandoned, secret NASA mission reveals why the U.S. has never returned to the moon.

701141.title: Tiburones en La Luna (Doblado)
701141.description: Durante la Guerra Fría, la URSS desarrolló tiburones hiperagresivos. Incapaces de matarlos, los líderes militares de la URSS lanzaron los tiburones a la luna.

701801.title: A Werewolf Boy (Subbed)
701801.description: Summoned by an unexpected phone call, a woman visits the cottage she used to live in as a child and recalls the memory of a boy she knew 47 years ago.

702003.title: I Think We're Alone Now
702003.description: The apocalypse proves to be a blessing in disguise for one lucky recluse—until a second survivor arrives with the threat of companionship.

707024.title: A Writer's Odyssey (Dubbed)
707024.description: Years after his child is abducted, a man is hired to kill the author of a fantasy novel, but the world of the novel seems to intersect with reality.

707331.title: Earth's Final Hours
707331.description: Freak radiation storms threaten to stop the Earth’s rotation. Does a disgraced inventor and an archaic satellite hold the key to humanity’s survival?

708476.title: Warning
708476.description: Mankind faces deadly consequences when a global storm causes the omniscient technology they created to malfunction in this sci-fi thriller.

710116.title: Deus: The Dark Sphere
710116.description: Sent to investigate a mysterious black sphere orbiting Mars, astronauts wake from 8 months of hibernation to discover a strange transmission.

710948.title: The Boxxx
710948.description: After accepting and smoking what seems like an average blunt from a coworker, Kevin suddenly finds himself thrust inside a world of lust and sex.

711946.title: A-X-L
711946.description: A top-secret killer robotic dog developed for the U.S. military develops a special friendship with Miles and will go to any lengths to protect him.

712853.title: The Moment After
712853.description: After a mass disappearance, two FBI agents are called in to investigate the strange occurrence, which may hold religious significance.

714354.title: The Astronaut's Wife
714354.description: After briefly losing consciousness during a space mission, an astronaut returns home as a chilling reality begins to set in for his doting wife.

715229.title: FernGully: The Last Rainforest
715229.description: The magical inhabitants of a rainforest must fight to save their home from the looming threat of a logging and a polluting force of destruction.

716866.title: Joe's Apartment
716866.description: A New York transplant rents a seedy apartment inhabited by thousands of singing, dancing cockroaches who help him woo a girl and avoid eviction.

722364.title: Absolute Zero
722364.description: After a shift in the Earth's polarity, one scientist races against time to stop Miami from being plunged into total darkness and -460 degree weather.

723394.title: What If…
723394.description: 15 years after leaving his ministry for a business opportunity, a man gets a chance to see what life would look like if he had followed his calling.

724426.title: The Philadelphia Experiment
724426.description: Two young seamen fall through a time warp to a different era and must return back before it sucks present-day earth back to the past.

724867.title: The Colony
724867.description: Forced underground by the next ice age, a struggling outpost of survivors fights to preserve humanity against a threat even more savage than nature.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000077.title: Grabbers
100000077.description: In this comic sci-fi thriller, the inhabitants of a small island discover they must get drunk in order to survive an invasion of bloodsucking aliens.

100000089.title: Enter the Void
100000089.description: An American drug dealer living in Tokyo takes a psychedelic, acid trip-like journey into the afterlife when he’s killed in a deal gone bad.

100000221.title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
100000221.description: A mysterious map sends the Smurfs on a thrilling race through a forbidden forest filled with magical creatures to find a forgotten hamlet.

100000302.title: Real Steel
100000302.description: In a near future where human boxers have been replaced by robots, a struggling ex-boxer and his estranged son reunite while training a robot fighter.

100000406.title: Star Slammer
100000406.description: Two women fight off lesbian guards, crazed wardens, and mutant rodents as they struggle to rally their fellow inmates and escape a prison planet.

100000487.title: Ghostbusters II
100000487.description: The superstars of the supernatural reunite to battle an enormous underground river of slime that threatens New York City in this hilarious sequel.

100000556.title: No Escape
100000556.description: A soldier convicted for murdering his commanding officer is dumped and left to die on a prison island inhabited by two camps of convicts.

100000784.title: Ghostbusters
100000784.description: A trio of failed university parapsychologists cash in on an uptick in New Yorkers’ paranormal complaints by setting up a ghost extermination service.

100001088.title: White Sky
100001088.description: Survivors of an alien invasion realize there’s nowhere to hide from the altered human beings that seem intent upon assimilating them.

100001208.title: The Objective
100001208.description: By the director of The Blair Witch Project comes this terrorist-thriller about a Special Ops group that is sent on a deadly mission to Afghanistan.

100001240.title: One Shot (Español)
100001240.description: Un francotirador que lucha contra un ejército alienígena debe elegir entre su propia vida y la vida de uno de los mismos seres que quiere matar.

100001267.title: Días De Un Perro (Doblado)
100001267.description: Antes de Navidad, un niño se encuentra en un terrible aprieto después de que su deseo de tener un perro sale mal y termina en el cuerpo de uno.

100001270.title: At the Earth's Core
100001270.description: When two explorers drive a large drill into the center of the Earth, they discover a hidden world where humans are enslaved by prehistoric beasts.

100001288.title: Meteor
100001288.description: An American scientist learns that a huge meteor is hurtling towards Earth, and the only way to stop it is to share nuclear secrets with the USSR.

100001293.title: The People That Time Forgot
100001293.description: In this epic adventure, an expedition searching for a lost explorer stumbles upon a strange oasis in the Arctic inhabited by dinosaurs and cavemen.

100001337.title: Radioflash
100001337.description: When an electromagnetic pulse cuts power across the Western US, a teenage girl and her father head into the woods to join her survivalist grandfather.

100001390.title: Tale of Tales
100001390.description: This inventive anthology film brings us three gory, gorgeous, grown-up stories of magic, monsters, and royalty based on Italian fairy tales.

100001394.title: Carnifex
100001394.description: On their quest into the Australian Outback to track the animals left displaced by bushfires, a trio discovers a terrifying species and realize they're the ones being tracked.

100001406.title: Critters
100001406.description: After escaping from a maximum-security prison asteroid, a band of extraterrestrial flesh-eating criminals unwittingly land on planet Earth.

100001423.title: The Adventures of Pinocchio
100001423.description: When a fairy brings one of puppet-maker Geppetto's creations magically to life, the wooden Pinocchio learns lessons as he tries to become a real boy.

100001453.title: The Tomorrow Job
100001453.description: A team of thieves encounters complications during a heist while using a time-travel drug that allows them to trade places with their future selves.

100001475.title: Doctor Dolittle
100001475.description: A workaholic doctor disrupts his family life and raises the concerns of his colleagues when he rediscovers his ability to communicate with animals.

100001476.title: RocketMan
100001476.description: An accident-prone computer programmer’s childhood dream comes true when he’s selected by NASA to join the first manned mission to Mars.

100001684.title: La Abominable Pitón (Doblado)
100001684.description: Un grupo de cineastas que filman en un pueblo abandonado descubren unos huevos y pronto se dan cuenta de que pertenecen a una enorme pitón.

100001687.title: Tiburón Terrestre (Doblado)
100001687.description: Un grupo científico que intenta modificar genéticamente un tiburón crea una máquina de matar destructiva que ni siquiera ellos pueden controlar.

100001829.title: Dr. Dolittle 2
100001829.description: Dr. Dolittle is back! This time around, he’s playing matchmaker for a lovesick circus bear and helping a community of forest animals save their home.

100001935.title: The Predator
100001935.description: When a young boy accidentally sparks a battle with genetically-enhanced aliens, a ragtag crew of ex-Marines bands together to save the human race.

100001965.title: Frankenstein vs. The Mummy
100001965.description: Mayhem ensues when the mummy of a cursed pharaoh is brought to the same university where a scientist is collecting body parts to reanimate a corpse.

100002073.title: Mr. Peabody & Sherman
100002073.description: A canine inventor and his human son travel through time to witness the most important events in history, but a rift in time endangers the future.

100002087.title: King Kong
100002087.description: A devious producer leads his crew to an ominous island full of deadly creatures, where a giant ape becomes captivated by the film’s leading lady.

100002156.title: Men in Black
100002156.description: Tasked with policing extraterrestrial activities on Earth, two agents join forces to track down a dangerous alien intent upon galactic destruction.

100002157.title: Men in Black II
100002157.description: In order to save the planet from an alien seductress disguised as a supermodel, Agent J must find a way to restore his former partner’s memories.

100002273.title: Geostorm
100002273.description: A system of satellites designed to control the climate goes haywire and sets off extreme weather events that threaten to destroy the world.

100002302.title: Men in Black 3
100002302.description: Agent J travels back in time to 1969, where he teams up with a younger version of Agent K to stop a time-hopping alien from destroying the future.

100002324.title: Life of Pi
100002324.description: En route to a new life in Canada, an Indian teen loses his family at sea and is set adrift for 227 days in a lifeboat with a 450-pound Bengal tiger.

100002552.title: Smallfoot
100002552.description: A bright young Yeti finds something he thought didn't exist—a human—throwing his Yeti community into an uproar over what else might be out there.

100002616.title: Along With the Gods: The Two Worlds
100002616.description: After dying unexpectedly, a man is taken to the afterlife, where he must pass seven trials and prove he lived a noble life in order to reincarnate.

100002666.title: Shadow Master
100002666.description: After being slain by a group of criminals, a man is reborn with animal-like superpowers and makes it his mission to right the wrongs of his city.

100002689.title: The Green Knight
100002689.description: King Arthur's headstrong nephew embarks on an epic, daring quest to confront the Green Knight, a mysterious giant who appears at Camelot.

100002866.title: The Device
100002866.description: Two estranged sisters reunite at their family cabin to spread their mother’s ashes, only to make a horrifying discovery in the woods.

100002882.title: The Amazing Spider-Man
100002882.description: Teenage outcast Peter Parker grapples with bullying at his high school and amazing super-human crises as his alter-ego, Spider-Man.

100002883.title: Ghost Rider
100002883.description: Years after superstar motorcycle stunt rider Johnny Blaze made a devil's bargain to protect his loved ones, Beelzebub returns for his due.

100002884.title: Ghost Rider: Spirit of Vengeance
100002884.description: Struggling to repress the Ghost Rider's curse, Johnny Blaze gets a chance at redemption when a secret sect recruits him to protect a boy from Satan.

100002888.description: An academic researcher opens a portal into a parallel universe and makes contact with his double in order to prevent an apocalypse.

100003015.title: Tomorrow, When the War Began
100003015.description: When their country is invaded and their families taken, eight Australian teenagers band together to become unlikely warriors in a fight for freedom.

100003156.title: Back to the Future
100003156.description: Marty McFly is blasted to 1955 in a time machine created by Doc Brown and finds himself in a time-shattering situation that jeopardizes his future.

100003157.title: Back to the Future Part II
100003157.description: Marty McFly and Doc Brown launch themselves to the year 2015 to fine-tune the future and inadvertently disrupt the spacetime continuum.

100003275.title: Back to the Future Part III
100003275.description: Marty McFly travels to 1885 to rescue Doc Brown and put the past, present, and future on track so they can all return to where they belong.

0300009901.title: Lovecraft Country
0300009901.description: Atticus Freema joins his friend Letitia and his uncle George to embark on a road trip across 1950's Jim Crow America in search of his missing father.

02067.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!
02067.description: Follows the adventures of teenager Yugi, whose magical secret comes to life when he plays his favorite card game: 'Duel Monsters.'

0300005160.title: The Triangle
0300005160.description: After a large number of cargo ships disappear into the Bermuda Triangle, a specialist team uncovers a truth more disturbing than mythical legend.

0300006947.title: Highway to Heaven
0300006947.description: An earthbound probationary angel and a skeptical ex-cop wander from town to town using heavenly wisdom and otherworldly powers to guide lost souls.

01075.title: Dresden Files
01075.description: Harry Dresden is just a private detective but with extraordinary abilities. Whether consulting for the police or following his own cases, he battles dark forces with a wry sense of humor.

02194.title: Earth: Final Conflict
02194.description: FROM LEGENDARY TV PRODUCER GENE RODDENBERRY of STAR TREK fame comes a thrilling, epic quest to save humanity. When an advanced alien species, the Taelons, comes to Earth in the early 21st century on a seemingly peaceful mission to share their knowledge and technology with humanity, they choose courageous Police Captain William Boon (Kevin Kilner) and his partner, Captain Lili Marquette (Lisa Howard), to be the protectors of their elected "Companion" to mankind, Da'an (Leni Parker). Boon quickly finds himself torn between his secretive new employers and an underground human resistance group that will do anything to uncover the Taelons' real motives. Roddenberry's last series is an intense adventure loaded with hair-raising action, cutting-edge technology, and unforgettable drama.

0300008835.title: Sanctuary
0300008835.description: As gene therapy, transplants and cloning offer hope for humanity, a dark side of evolution produces monsters a select few are brave enough to take on.

0300006624.title: I Dream of Jeannie
0300006624.description: A marooned astronaut finds a strange bottle on an island containing a beautiful Genie whose granted wishes, back at home, don’t quite come out right!

0300009966.title: The Twilight Zone
0300009966.description: In this revival of the classic anthology series, host Forest Whitaker leads us on a mysterious journey into the deepest recesses of the human psyche.

02230.title: Valkyrie Drive: Mermaid
02230.description: After adorable “mermaid” Mamori is transferred to one of five artificial islands, she’s cornered, attacked and eventually saved by another beautiful transfer named Mirei.

011.title: Transformers: Generation 1
011.description: Sentient robotic beings from Cybertron crash land on Earth, divided into two factions – the Autobots and Decepticons – as they both vie for Energon!

02192.title: Andromeda
02192.description: Civilization has fallen and one ship's crew has vowed to drive back the night and rekindle the light of civilization.

0300006705.title: Los Caballeros del Zodiaco: Hades (Doblado)
0300006705.description: No mucho después de la batalla entre los Caballeros y Poseidón, el dios del Inframundo Hades es resucitado y conspira para matar a Atenea y apoderarse del mundo. Con la ayuda de los Caballeros de Oro y Plata resucitados, Hades envía a su ejército para atacar el Santuario y capturar Atenea. Lo único que se interpone es Seiya y sus compañeros los Caballeros de Bronce.

04638.title: Dark Shadows
04638.description: The classic, gothic, daytime TV series about a tormented vampire, freed from his grave after 200 years, who returns home to protect his loved ones.

0300000158.title: Hemlock Grove
0300000158.description: As a once-vibrant and now struggling community’s secrets begin to unravel, Hemlock Grove forces us to ask: What is the true nature of a monster?

0300005039.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! (Español)
0300005039.description: Sigue las aventuras del estudiante de secundaria Yugi, que tiene un secreto mágico que cobra vida cuando juega 'Duel Monsters'.

0300010375.title: Invasion
0300010375.description: In this suspenseful tale, a blended family finds themselves at the center of a conspiracy designed to mask a massive alien takeover.

04211.title: Cinderella
04211.description: Lush adaptation of the fairy tale where a young and impoverished pianist finds her world of romance and magic in the streets of 1950’s Rome.

0300006608.title: Bewitched
0300006608.description: The beloved TV series about a beautiful witch who marries an executive and starts a family as a housewife, much to the dismay of her powerful mother.

0300006521.title: Silo
0300006521.description: Raised during the apocalypse in an underground home, a young man and his siblings must venture into a nuclear-active world filled with monsters.

01546.title: Wolfblood
01546.description: Being a teen is hard but being a Wolfblood is even more complicated as Maddy and the others try to keep their shape-shifting secret from the world.

0300010240.title: Tremors: The Series
0300010240.description: In the sleepy desert town of Perfection, Nevada, a no-nonsense survivalist struggles to maintain an uneasy peace with a giant prehistoric albino worm.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

04753.title: Beowulf: Return to the Shieldlands
04753.description: In a world of danger populated by both humans and fantastical creatures, Beowulf must slowly reconnect with the notion of family and home.

0300009559.title: Farscape
0300009559.description: Thrown into a distant part of the universe, an Earth astronaut finds himself part of a fugitive alien starship crew.

03254.title: The Prisoner
03254.description: After he resigns from his job, a secret agent is abducted and taken to what looks like an ideal village, except it is really a bizarre prison .

03744.title: Tin Man
03744.description: It’s a whole new yellow brick road as a mistress of evil with plans to come to Earth must face a rebellious, kind girl who sees visions in her dreams.

0300010083.title: The Tomorrow People
0300010083.description: A group of genetically advanced teens with paranormal abilities flee the agents of a paramilitary group on a mission to eradicate them.
